name: 9jacorp
description: An army of Nigerian Web Entrepreneurs
overview:
9jacorp is a Nigerian project focused on first, Nigerian and second, Africa and then the rest of the world. The aim of this project is to build African Internet Entrepreneurs in the area of Web Development, Social Media, Internet Business and Mobile Technology that will be a major player in the future of the web.

9jacorp’s aim is to make others succeed by giving the right values and excellent information/development services built on Web 2.0 and the future of web.
